152
00:07:40,020 --> 00:07:43,020
Usually in the form of numbers

153
00:07:43,020 --> 00:07:46,020
In classical physics, you often give...

154
00:07:46,020 --> 00:07:48,020
I will give you some examples, but...

155
00:07:48,020 --> 00:07:53,539
you usually give it in the form of real numbers

156
00:07:53,539 --> 00:07:57,400
the position, the velocity, a set of real numbers

